{"word":"H4043 - מָגֵן - mâgên - maw-gane' - [idiom] armed","slug":"H4043","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָגֵן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâgên"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-gane'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] armed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D2;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D2;&#x05DF; - ma&#x0302;ge&#x0302;n  m<sup>e</sup>ginna&#x0302;h</b> - <i>maw-gane', meg-in-naw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1598\">H1598</a>; a <i>shield</i> (that is, the small one or <i>buckler</i>); figuratively a <i>protector</i>; also the scaly <i>hide</i> of the crocodile: -  X armed, buckler, defence, ruler, + scale, shield."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1527\">H1527</a>, <a href=\"#/H1588\">H1588</a>, <a href=\"#/H1593\">H1593</a>, <a href=\"#/H1594\">H1594</a>, <a href=\"#/H1598\">H1598</a>, <a href=\"#/H1599\">H1599</a>, <a href=\"#/H4042\">H4042</a>, <a href=\"#/H4044\">H4044</a>"}]}